THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES

This project uses or is compatible with the following third-party libraries:

1. Swoole (Apache License 2.0)
   - https://github.com/swoole/swoole-src
   - Used for asynchronous coroutines and networking

2. bcg729 (GNU General Public License v3.0)
   - Original: https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/bcg729
   - PHP Extension: https://github.com/berzersks/bcg729
   - Optional: G.729 audio codec support

3. Opus Codec (BSD License)
   - Xiph.Org Foundation
   - https://opus-codec.org/
   - PHP Extension: https://github.com/berzersks/opus
   - Optional: Opus audio codec support

4. psampler
   - https://github.com/berzersks/psampler
   - Optional: Audio resampling utilities

Users must ensure compliance with the licenses of the original libraries when
using this software. The PHP extensions (bcg729, opus, psampler) maintain their
own licenses - consult individual repositories for details.

PROTOCOLS AND STANDARDS

This implementation is based on the following open standards:
- SIP: RFC 3261 (IETF)
- RTP/RTCP: RFC 3550 (IETF)
- SDP: RFC 4566 (IETF)
- DTMF: RFC 2833 (IETF)
